><br />\n我唔是呢種啊 只係想有人攬下我 聽下我講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉 點樣表達佢先會明我想要既野好簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔識<br />\n好想佢一直喺我身邊<br />\n利申 表達能力出名差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0165e402d1134bc7f88f340b63c3f45fcb25815b","tid":106291,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:11:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n其實我踩親你邊到....</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nblock左佢啦<br />\n佢心理變態架</blockquote><br />\nblock完好似佢都照comment到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你心情唔好<br />\n暫時唔適合睇佢d變態comment<br />\n佢照留言你睇唔到架"},{"pid":"a8d971d09cda276808f617d7d6396e81184761b0","tid":106291,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:12:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當自己抑鬱症愈嚴重 就愈想收埋自己<br />\n負面情緒好勁<br />\n但無渠道發洩 完全唔敢同另一半提起<br />\n搞到傾乜個人都嗯嗯哦哦咁<br />\n幾時先可以做正常人........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上lihkg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經上到上晒癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打係感情煩惱想死？"},{"pid":"9fd2bfc0caf38c7faa7b273b52845d99d09ec0ed","tid":106291,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:12:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當自己抑鬱症愈嚴重 就愈想收埋自己<br />\n負面情緒好勁<br />\n但無渠道發洩 完全唔敢同另一半提起<br />\n搞到傾乜個人都嗯嗯哦哦咁<br />\n幾時先可以做正常人........<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人有情緒病真係好麻煩<br />\n不過我覺得呢啲情況其實普遍人都有<br />\n試下放低一陣唔好咁上心不停諗住先<br />\n做下其他野分下心 <br />\n可能初頭幾個鐘都仲會不停諗<br />\n但一路做其他野時，自己情緒都會慢慢有啲轉變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時候係就算有傾得到<br />\n以為會好好多<br />\n點知更worse <br />\n就好似傾唔傾都sad咁</blockquote><br />\n傾個陣 <br />\n我因為有得傾而覺得好開心<br />\n但對方會有時會表現到唔想傾 沉默<br />\n我就比佢呢個行為整到好傷心<br />\n但我都無放棄 想珍惜傾計呢個行為<br />\n不斷搵話題 想開心咁一齊傾<br />\n最後換黎 《我傾得唔開心所以沉默表達》<br />\n而架覺得 情願唔傾都好過好似交功課咁傾<br />\n大家最後都唔開心"},{"pid":"86fdbfa1bdea37d65ad34faee3a5fc40b25ae5f8","tid":106291,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:12:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我唔是呢種啊 只係想有人攬下我 聽下我講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉 點樣表達佢先會明我想要既野好簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔識<br />\n好想佢一直喺我身邊<br />\n利申 表達能力出名差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁要返工返學架"},{"pid":"a708a447bca9f40b1f479688116ef83b78cce876","tid":106291,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:14:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>並唔係得你係咁 <br />\n你想發洩咩？ 我比車馬費你 你兜野踢我落去。成件事就係咁簡單</blockquote><br />\n我唔是呢種啊 只係想有人攬下我 聽下我講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉 點樣表達佢先會明我想要既野好簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔識<br />\n好想佢一直喺我身邊<br />\n利申 表達能力出名差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n表達能力真係好差<br />\n但我已經好盡力去表達我好愛佢<br />\n我好想佢陪我 我會聽哂佢話<br />\n但佢只係睇到我表達得唔好既野<br />\n見唔到我表達得好既野"},{"pid":"fffa3ce6f31bfdcdf63b1f7281fa58e9f9753e75","tid":106291,"uid":8351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:22:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\nblock左佢啦<br />\n佢心理變態架</blockquote><br />\nblock完好似佢都照comment到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你心情唔好<br />\n暫時唔適合睇佢d變態comment<br />\n佢照留言你睇唔到架</blockquote><br />\n其實佢啲comment好似我啲心聲<br />\n只係當係其他人講嘅時候<br />\n會更肯定自己廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68b975c41d76f5f7ea2a52ac3c89617663df87f","tid":106291,"uid":8351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:23:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上lihkg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n已經上到上晒癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打係感情煩惱想死？</blockquote><br />\n唔係單方面感情煩惱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2f9ff8d8d0c46f284085c9490670de4640743d","tid":106291,"uid":8351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:25:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n人有情緒病真係好麻煩<br />\n不過我覺得呢啲情況其實普遍人都有<br />\n試下放低一陣唔好咁上心不停諗住先<br />\n做下其他野分下心 <br />\n可能初頭幾個鐘都仲會不停諗<br />\n但一路做其他野時，自己情緒都會慢慢有啲轉變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有時候係就算有傾得到<br />\n以為會好好多<br />\n點知更worse <br />\n就好似傾唔傾都sad咁</blockquote><br />\n傾個陣 <br />\n我因為有得傾而覺得好開心<br />\n但對方會有時會表現到唔想傾 沉默<br />\n我就比佢呢個行為整到好傷心<br />\n但我都無放棄 想珍惜傾計呢個行為<br />\n不斷搵話題 想開心咁一齊傾<br />\n最後換黎 《我傾得唔開心所以沉默表達》<br />\n而架覺得 情願唔傾都好過好似交功課咁傾<br />\n大家最後都唔開心</blockquote><br />\n覺得你好似我另一半<br />\n有時我都好想傾<br />\n但唔知點解個人會down晒 dead晒air<br />\n好似傾都好頹<br />\n傾傾下就會連嘢都唔講"},{"pid":"b0f87418a88037d46fa1faefafb71bdb380e58e7","tid":106291,"uid":8351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:26:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n唉 點樣表達佢先會明我想要既野好簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔識<br />\n好想佢一直喺我身邊<br />\n利申 表達能力出名差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<b